snippet.title: Jumping Flash 2 - PS1 Longplay
snippet.description:
Jumping Flash 2
Developer: Exact
Publisher: Sony Computer Entertainment
Released: Aug 1996

1st Scenario just for fun.

As always, gaming is done on all official hardware and software. No emulation, no tool assistance, and no cheating!
We're not about speed runs, we're about having fun.

Watch live at http://www.twitch.tv/gamesquadsquad
Check out my NES repro blog at http://gameblorg.com/
